summary: The Story Of The Original Doge's Girlfriend - Kabosu's Era Is Over. Now It's Time To ChaCha! Kabosu, the adorable Shiba Inu who inspired the iconic Doge meme, shares a remarkable bond with his girlfriend, Cha-Cha. Their love story transcends the internet fame that Kabosu garnered, showcasing the deep connection and affection between two dogs.
